Right-click GoldSrc game in your Steam library and click Properties…. In the window that appears, under Launch Options, remove anything that’s in there and paste: -novid -nojoy -noipx

-novid - stops intro video with valve guy from playing, faster startup.

-nojoy - stops Joystick system from starting up, faster startup and less memory usage.

-noipx - stops ipx, ancient network protocol from starting up, possibly faster startup and less memory usage.
